title: Jonny Lieberman / Carlos Lago
description: Two of our favorite guests, Jonny Lieberman and Carlos Lago of MOTOR TREND, show up in the most 'Murica vehicles ever and create one of the funniest episodes yet. Topics include super cars, new Ferraris, selling Matt's Corvette (gasp), Carlos selling his 240 (bad idea), and how to gamble with Whiskey.
author: matt@thesmokingtire.com (Matt Farah & Zack Klapman)
